Josseline Gaël https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Josseline_Ga%C3%ABl 0 Josseline Gaël (born Jeannine Augustine Jeanne Blanleuil; 4 February 1917 – 10 August 1995) was a French film actress who specialised in comedy roles. Her daughter with Jules Berry, Michèle, became a renowned art dealer.
